# Local environment variables for Wrangler Pages Dev
# Rename this file to `.dev.vars` and input your keys.
# DO NOT commit the actual `.dev.vars` file to your git repository!

# (Optional) System-wide shared Gemini API key.
# If set, users will not need to input their own API key to generate motivational cards.
GEMINI_API_KEY="AIzaSyYourSystemGeminiKeyHere"
